Connectivity
============

There are many connectivity options available on the |product| industrial PC. It has 6 x USB Type A connectors configured as HOSTS, 1 x HDMI port, 1 x VGA, 2 x RJ45 connectors supporting Gigabit Ethernet (GbE), and 6 x RS232 connectors that can be configured in RS485 mode (2 x RS232 + 4 x RS485) as per request.

RS232/485 Connectors
-------------------------

Product has 6 x 9-pin D-Sub connectors which are configured as RS232 interfaces by default. The 4 ports: COM1~COM4, can be configured as either RS232 or RS485 communication interfaces through an internal convert board. If different configuration is required, please get in touch with Chipsee technical support at |email|_

  
